        "subject": "LU-2675 build: Fix build issue with lustre-core.m4",
        "message": "LU-2675 build: Fix build issue with lustre-core.m4\n\nWith the removal of lustre/include/linux the Makefile*\nwere removed but reference to these files remained in\nlustre-core.m4. This makes autogen.sh fail. We remove\nthe Makefile reference in lustre-core.m4 so autogen.sh\nworks again.\n\nChange-Id: Icd2993756a11d074b96033e84102e958e4e6dbd2\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\n"
      },
